working hard for you and our family.

280
00:14:38,513 --> 00:14:41,273
Now you're running away with your lover?

281
00:14:42,873 --> 00:14:44,153
Stop daydreaming.

282
00:14:50,194 --> 00:14:51,096
Forget about divorce.

283
00:14:52,074 --> 00:14:54,434
And you're not getting any of the money.

284
00:14:58,033 --> 00:14:58,834
When we

285
00:14:59,994 --> 00:15:00,793
settle the assets,

286
00:15:01,434 --> 00:15:02,714
don't blame me for being harsh.

287
00:15:06,273 --> 00:15:07,673
And one more thing.

288
00:15:08,273 --> 00:15:09,873
What you said was wrong.

289
00:15:11,114 --> 00:15:14,393
You said there's no love
in our marriage. That's not true.

290
00:15:14,793 --> 00:15:15,513
I'm telling you.

291
00:15:15,673 --> 00:15:17,633
I still love you. Do you believe me?

292
00:15:30,074 --> 00:15:30,793
Whatever.

293
00:15:34,354 --> 00:15:35,474
I'm ashamed to even say it.

294
00:15:42,153 --> 00:15:44,513
Once you've tasted the best,

295
00:15:45,114 --> 00:15:46,273
why insist on going back,

296
00:15:46,673 --> 00:15:47,673
settling for less?

297
00:15:49,873 --> 00:15:50,994
Maybe in the next life.

298
00:16:02,633 --> 00:16:03,594
Next life.

299
00:16:06,930 --> 00:16:11,256
(Qingzhou University, 2007)

300
00:16:12,314 --> 00:16:13,474
Guess what I did today.

301
00:16:14,074 --> 00:16:16,033
What did you do? You sound hyped.

302
00:16:16,474 --> 00:16:17,594
I went on a blind date.

303
00:16:18,114 --> 00:16:21,234
I'm telling you, my senior is amazing.

304
00:16:22,074 --> 00:16:23,594
He wears black-framed glasses

305
00:16:24,153 --> 00:16:25,673
and looks really scholarly.

306
00:16:26,153 --> 00:16:27,834
He talks about Borges all the time.

307
00:16:28,633 --> 00:16:29,954
He was into my friend...

308
00:16:33,114 --> 00:16:34,873
How much for these pants?

309
00:16:37,553 --> 00:16:38,714
And this one?

310
00:16:41,753 --> 00:16:43,594
How much for these two pairs of pants?

311
00:16:44,194 --> 00:16:45,114
They're not for sale.

312
00:16:45,114 --> 00:16:46,753
Why are you shouting?

313
00:16:46,753 --> 00:16:47,994
What's it to you?

314
00:16:48,074 --> 00:16:48,574
I...

315
00:16:50,673 --> 00:16:53,234
The phone you are calling
is powered off.

316
00:16:57,393 --> 00:16:59,864
The phone you are calling
is powered off.

317
00:17:00,504 --> 00:17:02,753
The phone you are calling
is powered off.

318
00:17:15,914 --> 00:17:19,634
The subscriber you dialed
is not answering.

319
00:17:20,033 --> 00:17:22,874
Still not answering?
You've called 100 times.

320
00:17:26,273 --> 00:17:27,353
Time for bed.

321
00:17:27,954 --> 00:17:29,313
Lights out.

322
00:17:53,874 --> 00:17:54,374
Hello?

323
00:17:54,753 --> 00:17:55,954
Where have you been?

324
00:17:56,434 --> 00:17:57,593
Why didn't you pick up?

325
00:17:58,113 --> 00:17:59,113
What do you want?

326
00:17:59,113 --> 00:18:01,113
My phone was off. What's it to you?

327
00:18:01,793 --> 00:18:02,714
What's wrong with you?

328
00:18:04,073 --> 00:18:05,593
Why are you so aggressive?

329
00:18:05,593 --> 00:18:06,914
What did I do to you?

330
00:18:08,234 --> 00:18:09,714
Don't you have a boyfriend now?

331
00:18:09,714 --> 00:18:12,474
You went on a blind date.
Take your anger out on him.

332
00:18:13,273 --> 00:18:14,113
What boyfriend?

333
00:18:14,914 --> 00:18:16,113
When did I get a boyfriend?

334
00:18:16,553 --> 00:18:17,994
What's with "Borges,"

335
00:18:18,154 --> 00:18:19,553
"glasses," and "scholarly"?

336
00:18:20,833 --> 00:18:21,753
Didn't you say that?

337
00:18:22,434 --> 00:18:23,513
Are you crazy?

338
00:18:24,234 --> 00:18:26,674
He's into the matchmaker, not me.

339
00:18:28,994 --> 00:18:29,833
What do you mean?

340
00:18:30,313 --> 00:18:32,474
It has nothing to do with you, anyway.

341
00:18:32,994 --> 00:18:34,434
So what if I had a boyfriend?

342
00:18:34,434 --> 00:18:36,914
Mind your own business.
Who do you think you are?

343
00:18:38,313 --> 00:18:38,813
Come on.

344
00:18:44,033 --> 00:18:46,793
The subscriber you dialed
is powered off.

345
00:18:47,434 --> 00:18:48,753
(Qingzhou, 2023)
I dare not mention this place.

346
00:18:48,874 --> 00:18:50,073
But you asked to meet here.

347
00:18:50,553 --> 00:18:51,434
What's wrong?

348
00:18:52,194 --> 00:18:53,553
Is there something superstitious?

349
00:18:54,353 --> 00:18:55,234
Is it creepy?

350
00:18:56,033 --> 00:18:56,833
Don't you remember

351
00:18:57,073 --> 00:18:59,434
where you met Liu Xiaoran?

352
00:19:02,914 --> 00:19:03,753
That's your fault.

353
00:19:04,313 --> 00:19:05,353
You introduced us.

354
00:19:05,593 --> 00:19:06,874
I'm holding you accountable.

355
00:19:07,553 --> 00:19:09,073
Fine, let's go there

356
00:19:09,553 --> 00:19:10,273
- for a drink.
- Get lost.

357
00:19:10,394 --> 00:19:11,154
Get lost.

358
00:19:11,714 --> 00:19:13,313
Let's talk business.

359
00:19:14,714 --> 00:19:15,353
Look.

360
00:19:15,914 --> 00:19:18,313
His lawyer sent me
your property division agreement.

361
00:19:23,394 --> 00:19:25,154
You two have too much shared property.

362
00:19:25,513 --> 00:19:27,113
Have you discussed how to divide it?

363
00:19:31,553 --> 00:19:33,474
How did I end up at this point?

364
00:19:37,154 --> 00:19:39,634
Ren Xiaoming, I'm asking you seriously.

365
00:19:40,073 --> 00:19:41,353
Other than Liu Xiaoran,

366
00:19:42,234 --> 00:19:44,394
is there anyone else?

367
00:19:47,833 --> 00:19:48,513
Who is he?

368
00:19:51,954 --> 00:19:53,954
(Qingzhou University, 2007)
My mom just went for the cheap stuff.

369
00:19:53,954 --> 00:19:55,513
This crappy down jacket

370
00:19:55,513 --> 00:19:57,513
is as thin as paper. I'm freezing.

371
00:19:57,571 --> 00:20:00,073
(Library)

372
00:20:00,073 --> 00:20:01,474
I have no other clothes.

373
00:20:02,033 --> 00:20:02,994
You will soon.

374
00:20:03,410 --> 00:20:04,312
(To Ren Xiaoming)

375
00:20:18,273 --> 00:20:20,234
Such a thick down jacket.

376
00:20:22,994 --> 00:20:23,914
Who bought it?

377
00:20:24,313 --> 00:20:25,353
Who gave it to you?

378
00:20:25,753 --> 00:20:27,353
It doesn't seem like your style.

379
00:20:27,353 --> 00:20:28,234
It looks nice.

380
00:20:29,313 --> 00:20:30,353
It looks pretty warm.

381
00:20:30,353 --> 00:20:30,914
Yeah.

382
00:20:31,113 --> 00:20:32,313
- It looks nice.
- Who gave it to you?

383
00:20:33,474 --> 00:20:34,234
Who gave it to you?

384
00:20:35,313 --> 00:20:37,753
That down jacket
you bought me is amazing.

385
00:20:38,353 --> 00:20:39,394
Why is it so thick?

386
00:20:39,954 --> 00:20:40,874
Is it a men's style?

387
00:20:43,194 --> 00:20:44,553
It feels like a steel plate.

388
00:20:46,793 --> 00:20:49,073
I like it.
I didn't say I didn't like it.

389
00:20:49,474 --> 00:20:51,273
It was freezing last night.

390
00:20:51,874 --> 00:20:53,273
When we came out of the library,

391
00:20:53,954 --> 00:20:55,833
those three were shivering.

392
00:20:56,113 --> 00:20:56,954
But,

393
00:20:57,634 --> 00:21:00,793
I was like a warrior
standing firm in the cold wind.

394
00:21:04,513 --> 00:21:05,474
How's your business?

395
00:21:09,073 --> 00:21:11,793
You fool.

396
00:21:12,634 --> 00:21:14,714
Who wears a dress like that
in this weather?

397
00:21:17,833 --> 00:21:19,154
You fool.

398
00:21:19,553 --> 00:21:21,593
Chatting with your boyfriend again?

399
00:21:21,753 --> 00:21:23,033
How sweet.

400
00:21:23,194 --> 00:21:25,513
Stop talking nonsense. He's my buddy.

401
00:21:25,994 --> 00:21:26,833
Who'd believe that?

402
00:21:27,154 --> 00:21:28,674
So attached to your buddy?

403
00:21:29,194 --> 00:21:30,954
You're adults now. Just admit it.

404
00:21:30,954 --> 00:21:31,593
Hypocrite.

405
00:21:31,593 --> 00:21:32,474
I must lower my voice.

406
00:21:32,474 --> 00:21:33,313
They can hear me.

407
00:21:34,434 --> 00:21:35,288
Stupid mosquito net.

408
00:21:37,353 --> 00:21:38,113
I heard

409
00:21:38,674 --> 00:21:39,434
there's a guy...

410
00:21:40,154 --> 00:21:40,874
Seen the news?

411
00:21:41,474 --> 00:21:42,194
I don't care.

412
00:21:42,434 --> 00:21:43,033
Okay?

413
00:21:50,914 --> 00:21:52,833
Ren Xiaoming, you dummy.

414
00:21:52,994 --> 00:21:53,714
Keep it down.

415
00:21:54,154 --> 00:21:54,994
Keep it down.

416
00:21:55,394 --> 00:21:58,553
With EQ like yours,
you deserve to be single forever.

417
00:21:58,674 --> 00:22:00,234
What's wrong with my EQ?

418
00:22:00,234 --> 00:22:02,994
I'd never been in a relationship.
It was my first time.

419
00:22:03,273 --> 00:22:04,954
Why should I know what guys think?

420
00:22:08,513 --> 00:22:09,474
So,

421
00:22:10,113 --> 00:22:13,714
he is your first love
Liu Xiaoran mentioned.

422
00:22:15,033 --> 00:22:16,113
There was a guy.

423
00:22:19,674 --> 00:22:21,194
Where is he now?

424
00:22:21,833 --> 00:22:23,513
You're still in contact.

425
00:22:24,234 --> 00:22:26,474
And you transfer money to him, right?

426
00:22:30,033 --> 00:22:33,553
I'm your lawyer.
I need you to tell me the truth.

427
00:22:35,553 --> 00:22:36,113
Let's go.

428
00:22:45,010 --> 00:22:47,122
(No. 6 Hospital)

429
00:22:53,033 --> 00:22:53,793
Ms. Ren.

430
00:23:00,194 --> 00:23:01,313
Bai Shu?

431
00:23:07,394 --> 00:23:08,954
You're Bai Shu?

432
00:23:11,073 --> 00:23:11,714
Well,

433
00:23:12,674 --> 00:23:13,674
how have you been?

434
00:23:14,273 --> 00:23:15,874
Where have you been all these years?

435
00:23:16,434 --> 00:23:17,874
I haven't heard from you at all.

436
00:23:20,793 --> 00:23:22,753
I asked Xiaoming many times
where you were.

437
00:23:22,914 --> 00:23:24,313
She wouldn't say anything.

438
00:23:26,353 --> 00:23:27,833
Why did you stop visiting?

439
00:23:30,033 --> 00:23:31,234
You two fell out?

440
00:23:33,313 --> 00:23:35,033
Did Xiaoming upset you?

441
00:23:36,154 --> 00:23:38,033
I know she could be stubborn.

442
00:23:39,994 --> 00:23:41,874
Why didn't you
go to Qingzhou University?

443
00:23:42,234 --> 00:23:45,113
You were such a good student.
Xiaoming wasn't as good as you.

444
00:23:45,634 --> 00:23:47,753
She got in. Why didn't you?

445
00:23:53,113 --> 00:23:56,634
It's fine if you don't want to talk.
It's just good to see you.

446
00:23:59,513 --> 00:24:01,113
I haven't seen you in 16 years.

447
00:24:03,793 --> 00:24:05,194
Yuxiu.

448
00:24:05,994 --> 00:24:08,553
Your student Bai Shu is here to see you.

449
00:24:08,833 --> 00:24:10,234
Do you remember her?

450
00:24:10,753 --> 00:24:13,513
She was the top student in your class.

451
00:24:14,313 --> 00:24:16,273
(Clue)
The story of this novel mainly revolves

452
00:24:16,273 --> 00:24:18,353
around the growth of two girls.

453
00:24:18,513 --> 00:24:20,234
The characters we've identified

454
00:24:20,234 --> 00:24:22,073
are Ren Xiaoming and Bai Shu.

455
00:24:22,394 --> 00:24:23,273
In the novel,

456
00:24:23,273 --> 00:24:26,753
their lives largely overlapped
before they went to the university.

457
00:24:27,194 --> 00:24:29,073
All the characters that appeared

458
00:24:29,273 --> 00:24:31,674
have been checked.

459
00:24:31,954 --> 00:24:32,954
But not a single person

460
00:24:33,033 --> 00:24:35,513
could be the deceased
in Leopard and Graveyard.

461
00:24:35,714 --> 00:24:37,914
Therefore, the deceased must appear

462
00:24:37,914 --> 00:24:40,113
in the plot
after the two girls went to university.

463
00:24:40,273 --> 00:24:41,513
In reality,

464
00:24:41,593 --> 00:24:43,553
Ren Xiaoming and Bai Shu

465
00:24:43,714 --> 00:24:44,954
took two different paths.

466
00:24:45,313 --> 00:24:47,234
Now, we need to split into two teams.

467
00:24:47,353 --> 00:24:48,353
Huang Yue and I

468
00:24:48,353 --> 00:24:49,474
will investigate Bai Shu.

469
00:24:49,474 --> 00:24:50,194
Shun,

470
00:24:50,313 --> 00:24:51,033
you and Yanzi

471
00:24:51,353 --> 00:24:52,353
investigate Ren Xiaoming.

472
00:24:52,674 --> 00:24:53,833
We'll investigate

473
00:24:53,833 --> 00:24:55,273
all related personnel.

474
00:24:55,313 --> 00:24:56,833
Meanwhile, we must also

475
00:24:56,833 --> 00:24:59,073
keep an eye on Ren Xiaoming and Bai Shu.

476
00:24:59,234 --> 00:24:59,914
Got it?

477
00:25:00,154 --> 00:25:01,033
- Got it.
- Got it.

478
00:25:01,474 --> 00:25:02,033
Let's go.

479
00:25:02,130 --> 00:25:04,024
(Breathe, Shu)

480
00:25:05,874 --> 00:25:06,374
Bai Shu.

481
00:25:10,954 --> 00:25:11,674
What's the rush?

482
00:25:11,874 --> 00:25:12,674
Need something?

483
00:25:13,394 --> 00:25:14,360
I finished the novel.

484
00:25:15,593 --> 00:25:17,273
Is it the same as the diary

485
00:25:17,634 --> 00:25:18,394
you mentioned?

486
00:25:18,994 --> 00:25:19,793
Is it all true?

487
00:25:21,434 --> 00:25:23,113
A diary records real events.

488
00:25:23,674 --> 00:25:24,593
If it's fake,

489
00:25:25,634 --> 00:25:26,714
what's the point?

490
00:25:27,353 --> 00:25:28,954
Too bad I don't have that diary.

491
00:25:29,914 --> 00:25:31,313
"The Dark Side of the Moon"

492
00:25:32,273 --> 00:25:33,073
is also true?

493
00:25:37,778 --> 00:25:42,057
(La City, 2007)

494
00:25:42,113 --> 00:25:42,613
Shu.

495
00:25:43,513 --> 00:25:44,273
Why are you here?

496
00:25:44,753 --> 00:25:45,593
I'm waiting for you.

497
00:25:47,033 --> 00:25:47,674
Get in.

498
00:25:50,154 --> 00:25:51,234
You know me well.

499
00:25:51,634 --> 00:25:54,073
Is it necessary
to keep such a safe distance?

500
00:25:56,674 --> 00:25:57,474
Need something?

501
00:25:57,954 --> 00:25:59,073
Yeah, of course.

502
00:25:59,394 --> 00:26:00,553
I'm here to thank you.

503
00:26:00,954 --> 00:26:02,434
The translation you did for me

504
00:26:03,073 --> 00:26:04,634
saved me a lot of money.

505
00:26:05,113 --> 00:26:07,833
Plus, the translations were excellent.

506
00:26:08,234 --> 00:26:10,194
The foreign client compared

507
00:26:10,954 --> 00:26:11,954
several translation works

508
00:26:12,154 --> 00:26:14,833
and chose our translated manual
in the end.

509
00:26:15,793 --> 00:26:16,434
Really?

510
00:26:16,914 --> 00:26:17,414
Yeah.

511
00:26:17,833 --> 00:26:18,513
That's great.

512
00:26:19,234 --> 00:26:20,313
But don't thank me.

513
00:26:20,714 --> 00:26:22,634
I was paid for it, after all.

514
00:26:24,474 --> 00:26:26,793
You mentioned your company HQ
was in Singapore.

515
00:26:27,154 --> 00:26:27,833
That was later.

516
00:26:29,234 --> 00:26:30,474
Back when I was in Africa,

517
00:26:31,434 --> 00:26:32,793
the factory building got bombed.

518
00:26:34,194 --> 00:26:36,474
I lost my wife and child.

519
00:26:38,954 --> 00:26:39,593
After that,

520
00:26:40,593 --> 00:26:43,474
I took the little money I had left
and went to Southeast Asia.

521
00:26:48,474 --> 00:26:49,273
This is Niuniu.

522
00:26:50,634 --> 00:26:51,313
My daughter.

523
00:26:52,634 --> 00:26:53,944
She would have been your age.

524
00:26:58,874 --> 00:26:59,914
When I lost her,

525
00:27:02,593 --> 00:27:04,194
I truly felt the pain

526
00:27:05,154 --> 00:27:06,753
your mother felt losing her daughter.

527
00:27:10,474 --> 00:27:12,553
You'll never forget your dead children.

528
00:27:14,033 --> 00:27:14,674
What about me?

529
00:27:16,553 --> 00:27:19,753
My parents are alive.
Why didn't they look for me?

530
00:27:22,073 --> 00:27:25,593
Shu, I promised to help you find them.

531
00:27:26,394 --> 00:27:27,154
I'll do my best.

532
00:27:28,194 --> 00:27:29,194
Why are you helping me?

533
00:27:31,234 --> 00:27:31,874
Actually,

534
00:27:32,954 --> 00:27:34,194
I'm helping your mom too.

535
00:27:35,113 --> 00:27:37,273
I was only sixteen and small

536
00:27:37,634 --> 00:27:40,194
for my age back then.

537
00:27:40,994 --> 00:27:42,113
So I was getting bullied.

538
00:27:42,634 --> 00:27:44,234
Your mom stood up for me.

539
00:27:44,753 --> 00:27:47,073
She was like a big sister
and a big brother,

540
00:27:47,553 --> 00:27:49,434
protecting me in everything.

541
00:27:50,113 --> 00:27:50,914
You liked her?

542
00:27:55,073 --> 00:27:55,994
A secret crush.

543
00:27:57,513 --> 00:27:58,273
My first love.

544
00:28:00,273 --> 00:28:01,394
Don't tell her that.

545
00:28:04,353 --> 00:28:07,353
Don't worry.
You know how it is between us.

546
00:28:08,234 --> 00:28:09,273
I wouldn't tell her.

547
00:28:12,793 --> 00:28:13,833
If this keeps up,

548
00:28:15,234 --> 00:28:16,593
she will lose you forever.

549
00:28:19,154 --> 00:28:20,313
I'll try my best to help you.

550
00:28:22,714 --> 00:28:23,474
Thank you.

551
00:28:24,273 --> 00:28:25,954
But I want to become strong

552
00:28:26,434 --> 00:28:29,073
not to understand her, but to leave her.

553
00:28:31,553 --> 00:28:32,474
Anything else?

554
00:28:33,593 --> 00:28:36,073
I've said what I needed to.

555
00:28:38,033 --> 00:28:40,113
It's getting late. Let me take you home.

556
00:28:40,434 --> 00:28:40,994
No need.

557
00:28:41,313 --> 00:28:42,613
Don't be shy. Come on.

558
00:28:42,613 --> 00:28:43,613
Let's go. Hurry.

559
00:29:00,434 --> 00:29:01,033
Bai Shu.

560
00:29:02,593 --> 00:29:03,113
Get in.

561
00:29:06,073 --> 00:29:06,634
Why?

562
00:29:07,234 --> 00:29:08,408
I got news from Wuchuan.

563
00:29:09,394 --> 00:29:10,593
Hurry up. Get in.

564
00:29:14,434 --> 00:29:15,154
Hurry up.

565
00:29:22,753 --> 00:29:23,273
Shu.

566
00:29:24,434 --> 00:29:27,032
Give me your ID card. I will have
the secretary book your flight.

567
00:29:28,113 --> 00:29:29,353
I don't have an ID card.

568
00:29:31,234 --> 00:29:33,273
She never lets me keep it myself.

569
00:29:33,954 --> 00:29:35,832
She locks up
the household registration, too.

570
00:29:39,194 --> 00:29:40,513
She wasn't like this before.

571
00:29:40,874 --> 00:29:43,234
She loved helping people, especially me.

572
00:29:44,954 --> 00:29:46,008
Can we not talk about her?

573
00:29:48,353 --> 00:29:49,394
I don't have an ID card.

574
00:29:49,994 --> 00:29:52,634
Is there another way for us
to get to Wuchuan?

575
00:29:54,234 --> 00:29:55,154
I'll drive you there.

576
00:29:56,113 --> 00:29:59,994
It's just a thousand-kilometer drive.
It'll be tough on you.

577
00:30:00,954 --> 00:30:01,634
I don't mind.

578
00:30:02,273 --> 00:30:03,874
Steal the household registration

579
00:30:04,674 --> 00:30:06,552
and get an ID card
at the police station later.

580
00:30:07,394 --> 00:30:09,593
Without an ID card,
you can't go anywhere.

581
00:30:14,002 --> 00:30:17,240
(Wuchuan City)

582
00:30:18,593 --> 00:30:20,113
Since you don't have your ID card,

583
00:30:20,714 --> 00:30:22,394
I can't get you a separate room.

584
00:30:23,313 --> 00:30:25,073
Luckily, they have one suite left.

585
00:30:30,874 --> 00:30:31,513
Go ahead.

586
00:30:34,674 --> 00:30:36,793
This suite has two bedrooms.

587
00:30:38,394 --> 00:30:39,234
Pick one.

588
00:30:44,674 --> 00:30:45,353
This one, then.

589
00:30:45,874 --> 00:30:46,374
Okay.

590
00:31:35,914 --> 00:31:36,513
What's wrong?

591
00:31:37,674 --> 00:31:38,434
You can't sleep?

592
00:31:50,113 --> 00:31:53,553
Good thing I'm a chronic insomniac
who carries sleeping pills.

593
00:31:56,914 --> 00:31:57,634
Remember.

594
00:31:58,394 --> 00:31:59,474
If you really can't sleep,

595
00:31:59,474 --> 00:32:00,194
take half a pill.

596
00:32:06,073 --> 00:32:06,914
Does it work?

597
00:32:07,474 --> 00:32:08,273
Try it.

598
00:32:09,033 --> 00:32:09,593
Thanks.

599
00:32:10,513 --> 00:32:11,273
Anything else?

600
00:32:13,313 --> 00:32:14,113
Then...

601
00:32:14,753 --> 00:32:15,353
Goodnight.

602
00:32:15,753 --> 00:32:16,353
Goodnight.

603
00:32:55,954 --> 00:32:56,593
Where is she?

604
00:33:08,553 --> 00:33:11,434
I was afraid she couldn't sleep,
so I gave her a sleeping pill.

605
00:33:20,154 --> 00:33:20,753
Come in.

606
00:33:24,073 --> 00:33:24,714
Come in.

607
00:33:26,313 --> 00:33:27,033
Close the door.

608
00:33:33,313 --> 00:33:34,634
Why did you do this?

609
00:33:35,394 --> 00:33:36,154
She's grown up.

610
00:33:37,194 --> 00:33:38,634
You can't keep her locked up.

611
00:33:39,714 --> 00:33:41,234
Let her make her own choices.

612
00:33:42,434 --> 00:33:43,634
The more you let go,

613
00:33:43,954 --> 00:33:45,313
the more she'll appreciate it.

614
00:33:46,833 --> 00:33:49,113
Are you teaching me how to be a mother?

615
00:33:50,154 --> 00:33:51,674
I'm doing this for your own good.

616
00:33:53,793 --> 00:33:55,113
Without saying a word,

617
00:33:55,833 --> 00:33:57,113
you took my child away.

618
00:33:59,313 --> 00:34:00,954
Is this for my own good?

619
00:34:03,234 --> 00:34:04,194
Eighteen years ago,

620
00:34:05,273 --> 00:34:07,474
I shouldn't have
come with you to pick up the child.

621
00:34:09,394 --> 00:34:10,633
I brought Bai Shu back,

622
00:34:11,593 --> 00:34:12,914
hoping you'd get better.

623
00:34:13,794 --> 00:34:16,113
But instead, you sank deeper.

624
00:34:20,354 --> 00:34:21,314
"Eighteen years ago"?

625
00:34:23,233 --> 00:34:24,153
"Pick up the child"?

626
00:34:25,954 --> 00:34:26,794
Nonsense.

627
00:34:30,394 --> 00:34:31,474
What's wrong with you?

628
00:34:32,633 --> 00:34:33,633
You're talking nonsense.

629
00:34:34,474 --> 00:34:35,553
Are you crazy?

630
00:34:38,834 --> 00:34:39,994
Let's see a doctor.

631
00:34:42,073 --> 00:34:44,033
I'll take you to the best doctor, okay?

632
00:34:44,713 --> 00:34:46,914
I'll tell everyone we know

633
00:34:48,713 --> 00:34:49,673
that I've treated you

634
00:34:50,673 --> 00:34:53,513
like my own younger brother
since childhood.

635
00:34:53,794 --> 00:34:54,553
But you

636
00:34:55,834 --> 00:34:57,394
stole my underwear.

637
00:34:59,233 --> 00:35:00,153
You're a lunatic.

638
00:35:02,553 --> 00:35:05,233
What are you saying? You're my sister.

639
00:35:07,354 --> 00:35:09,233
I've long considered you
a family member.

640
00:35:09,914 --> 00:35:10,954
What's wrong with you?

641
00:35:22,874 --> 00:35:23,374
Get up.

642
00:35:23,513 --> 00:35:24,553
You, go to that room.

643
00:35:24,633 --> 00:35:25,133
Get up.

644
00:35:25,834 --> 00:35:26,334
Get up.

645
00:35:32,474 --> 00:35:34,233
Don't be scared.
Your mom called the police.

646
00:35:34,394 --> 00:35:35,754
Were you assaulted?

647
00:35:36,593 --> 00:35:37,233
No, I wasn't.

648
00:35:38,233 --> 00:35:38,994
She's lying.

649
00:35:40,073 --> 00:35:41,513
He's the one lying.

650
00:35:42,113 --> 00:35:43,754
He offered to find your parents

651
00:35:43,994 --> 00:35:45,834
to lure you here and drug you

652
00:35:46,354 --> 00:35:46,854
just to

653
00:35:46,874 --> 00:35:48,513
- Shut up.
- do those things to you.

654
00:35:52,394 --> 00:35:52,994
It's true.

655
00:35:54,954 --> 00:35:55,673
Wang Hao.

656
00:35:56,513 --> 00:35:57,633
Wang Hao, did you trick me?

657
00:35:58,153 --> 00:36:00,274
Weren't you taking me
to find my birth parents?

658
00:36:00,553 --> 00:36:03,113
You promised we'd go to the orphanage
tomorrow morning.

659
00:36:03,754 --> 00:36:06,314
Wang Hao, say something.

660
00:36:06,314 --> 00:36:07,274
Tell them.

661
00:36:07,593 --> 00:36:08,233
Enough.

662
00:36:08,513 --> 00:36:09,153
Enough.

663
00:36:12,233 --> 00:36:12,733
Be good.

664
00:36:22,513 --> 00:36:24,713
A man not much older than your dad.

665
00:36:26,633 --> 00:36:27,994
A married man.

666
00:36:29,994 --> 00:36:31,274
Isn't his wife dead?

667
00:36:32,113 --> 00:36:32,834
Dead?

668
00:36:36,033 --> 00:36:37,994
I had dinner with her last week.

669
00:36:40,274 --> 00:36:41,112
Her name's Zhou Na.

670
00:36:44,394 --> 00:36:44,954
It's funny?

671
00:36:46,754 --> 00:36:47,754
Aren't you disgusted?

672
00:36:50,713 --> 00:36:51,608
Insufficient evidence?

673
00:36:53,474 --> 00:36:54,673
I wish I could kill him.

674
00:37:01,754 --> 00:37:03,193
Can I go back to school now?

675
00:37:06,474 --> 00:37:07,113
Sure.

676
00:37:09,033 --> 00:37:10,633
But if you cause any more trouble,

677
00:37:11,513 --> 00:37:12,874
forget about going to school.

678
00:37:22,073 --> 00:37:22,874
Ms. Zhang.

679
00:37:23,673 --> 00:37:25,314
Excuse me, Ms. Zhang.

680
00:37:25,834 --> 00:37:29,274
Why isn't my name
on the vacation accommodation list?

681
00:37:29,754 --> 00:37:30,553
Did you register?

682
00:37:30,553 --> 00:37:32,233
I did. I told the dorm supervisor.

683
00:37:32,553 --> 00:37:34,073
Not with your faculty?

684
00:37:34,274 --> 00:37:37,033
They don't have you on the list.
So I can't put your name down.

685
00:37:37,593 --> 00:37:39,113
Register with the faculty?

686
00:37:39,474 --> 00:37:40,513
Is it too late now?

687
00:37:40,633 --> 00:37:42,113
There's only one week left.

688
00:37:42,474 --> 00:37:43,673
Who am I supposed to

689
00:37:44,033 --> 00:37:45,633
get to approve it now?

690
00:37:46,593 --> 00:37:48,033
Where am I supposed to stay?

691
00:37:48,673 --> 00:37:49,874
Can't you just go home?

692
00:37:50,314 --> 00:37:52,033
Your parents
haven't seen you for months.

693
00:37:52,354 --> 00:37:55,314
You want to stay in Qingzhou
to fool around, don't you?

694
00:37:55,314 --> 00:37:56,354
That's not true.

695
00:37:58,193 --> 00:38:00,073
I've lined up several jobs
for the vacation.

696
00:38:00,354 --> 00:38:02,274
Forget the jobs. Just go home.

697
00:38:09,074 --> 00:38:11,026
(Qidaohezi Railway Station)

698
00:38:11,122 --> 00:38:14,322
(Youth Civilization Train)

699
00:38:20,834 --> 00:38:21,713
I'll do it.

700
00:38:33,010 --> 00:38:37,266
(Qidaohezi Railway Station welcomes you.
Wishing you a safe journey.)

701
00:38:51,233 --> 00:38:52,513
Good dogs stay out of the way.

702
00:38:52,513 --> 00:38:53,033
Move.

703
00:38:54,394 --> 00:38:55,394
Bad dogs charge ahead.

704
00:38:55,513 --> 00:38:56,354
What's your problem?

705
00:38:56,474 --> 00:38:58,233
What's your problem?
You never answer my calls.

706
00:38:58,994 --> 00:39:00,713
Why should I answer your calls?

707
00:39:00,994 --> 00:39:03,113
Fine, we shouldn't be buddies anymore.

708
00:39:03,434 --> 00:39:05,193
Fine, let's cut ties.

709
00:39:05,874 --> 00:39:06,394
My bag.

710
00:39:06,874 --> 00:39:07,794
Give me my bag.

711
00:39:08,314 --> 00:39:08,914
Give it back.

712
00:39:10,354 --> 00:39:11,593
Will you be my girlfriend?

713
00:39:20,233 --> 00:39:20,914
Take it.

714
00:39:23,593 --> 00:39:25,593
I only have two arms.
Can't you carry one?

715
00:39:25,794 --> 00:39:27,434
Who makes his girlfriend carry the bags?

716
00:39:38,354 --> 00:39:40,633
Fine, don't carry anything. Slow down.

717
00:39:43,153 --> 00:39:44,113
Hurry up.

718
00:39:46,673 --> 00:39:47,553
You got this?

719
00:39:51,914 --> 00:39:53,274
They're so heavy.

720
00:40:24,193 --> 00:40:26,834
Go back. There are eyes everywhere.

721
00:40:27,553 --> 00:40:28,834
Why should I leave?

722
00:40:29,274 --> 00:40:32,033
I'm your boyfriend now.
Take me upstairs?

723
00:40:33,954 --> 00:40:34,914
Go away.

724
00:40:35,113 --> 00:40:35,832
Give it to me.

725
00:40:39,874 --> 00:40:40,794
Go away.

726
00:40:42,633 --> 00:40:44,193
Can I kiss you?

727
00:40:48,113 --> 00:40:49,334
I meant holding...

728
00:40:49,434 --> 00:40:50,834
I have an accent.

729
00:41:00,394 --> 00:41:03,233
You're carrying such heavy stuff.

730
00:41:04,394 --> 00:41:05,633
Stop messing around.

731
00:41:07,113 --> 00:41:08,033
My bag is falling.

732
00:41:08,033 --> 00:41:09,874
- Xiaoming...
- Can I carry you

733
00:41:09,874 --> 00:41:10,794
- and the stuff together?
- Xiaoming.

734
00:41:17,713 --> 00:41:18,274
Xiaoming.

735
00:41:24,633 --> 00:41:25,314
Hurry up.

736
00:41:26,394 --> 00:41:27,274
Come help me.

737
00:41:32,073 --> 00:41:32,794
Take this.

738
00:41:34,314 --> 00:41:35,233
Who was that?

739
00:41:37,113 --> 00:41:38,233
W-Who was that just now?

740
00:41:38,874 --> 00:41:39,553
Nobody.

741
00:41:45,633 --> 00:41:46,794
You've grown taller.

742
00:41:47,593 --> 00:41:49,434
You should think twice
before hitting me.

743
00:41:50,274 --> 00:41:51,354
I should think twice?

744
00:41:53,553 --> 00:41:55,113
About hitting you?

745
00:41:56,193 --> 00:41:57,274
Try fighting back.

746
00:42:00,314 --> 00:42:01,474
Xiaoming is back.

747
00:42:01,474 --> 00:42:03,033
You're back.

748
00:42:05,834 --> 00:42:07,354
- Food is ready.
- Guo Bao Rou.

749
00:42:11,354 --> 00:42:13,073
Were you starving? Go wash your hands.

750
00:42:13,553 --> 00:42:14,633
No table manners at all.

751
00:42:16,994 --> 00:42:19,274
How come your mom
hasn't improved at all?

752
00:42:20,794 --> 00:42:22,314
Isn't she your mom too?

753
00:42:23,153 --> 00:42:24,376
What are you saying about me?

754
00:42:25,914 --> 00:42:26,994
That you're beautiful.

755
00:42:27,274 --> 00:42:29,954
I haven't seen you for so long.
How are you still so pretty?

756
00:42:30,394 --> 00:42:32,633
Okay, that tuition was worth it.

757
00:42:33,354 --> 00:42:35,033
You came back as a changed person.

758
00:42:35,274 --> 00:42:35,874
Sit.

759
00:42:38,633 --> 00:42:39,153
Here.

760
00:42:39,713 --> 00:42:40,354
It's for you.

761
00:42:41,513 --> 00:42:42,073
All yours.

762
00:42:42,233 --> 00:42:43,874
Mind your manners.

763
00:42:44,754 --> 00:42:45,254
Here.

764
00:42:45,314 --> 00:42:45,834
Thanks, Mom.

765
00:42:48,713 --> 00:42:49,513
Xiaoming, have it.

766
00:42:50,354 --> 00:42:52,233
Try the dumplings. They are good.

767
00:42:52,233 --> 00:42:53,553
They're really good.

768
00:42:55,434 --> 00:42:56,474
Mom, dig in.

769
00:43:00,193 --> 00:43:01,033
Tasty, huh?

770
00:43:01,394 --> 00:43:02,914
Nothing beats home-cooked food.

771
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:12,808
=Vanished Name=
